Tattha katamaṃ sabbaṃ rūpaṃ? Cattāro ca mahābhūtā, catunnañca mahābhūtānaṃ upādāya rūpaṃ – idaṃ vuccati sabbaṃ rūpaṃ. Sabbaṃ rūpaṃ na hetu, ahetukaṃ, hetuvippayuttaṃ, sappaccayaṃ , saṅkhataṃ, rūpaṃrūpiyaṃ 
